{"tid":1916564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"意大利單日增133死　累計7375宗超韓國　成全球第二多病例國家","createTime":"2020-03-09T02:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T12:04:34.000Z","uid":241764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"915d4c9c93b58b9b28360bd0783fee88a9ff97b2","tid":1916564,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:58:26.000Z","msg":"意大利新型冠狀病毒疫情持續擴大，周日（8日）新增133宗死亡病例，累計366人死；確診病例同日新增1492宗，累計7375宗，確診個案數目超越韓國，成為中國以外全球第二多病例的國家。<br />\n<br />\n意大利陸軍總參謀長法利納（Salvatore Farina）確診感染新型冠狀病毒，他表示目前情況良好，正在住所自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200309/s00005/1583712701180/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%84%8f%e5%a4%a7%e5%88%a9%e5%96%ae%e6%97%a5%e5%a2%9e133%e6%ad%bb-%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%887375%e5%ae%97%e8%b6%85%e9%9f%93%e5%9c%8b-%e6%88%90%e5%85%a8%e7%90%83%e7%ac%ac%e4%ba%8c%e5%a4%9a%e7%97%85%e4%be%8b%e5%9c%8b%e5%ae%b6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200309%2Fs00005%2F1583712701180%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%2584%258f%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%2588%25a9%25e5%2596%25ae%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%25a2%259e133%25e6%25ad%25bb-%25e7%25b4%25af%25e8%25a8%25887375%25e5%25ae%2597%25e8%25b6%2585%25e9%259f%2593%25e5%259c%258b-%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%2585%25a8%25e7%2590%2583%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25ba%258c%25e5%25a4%259a%25e7%2597%2585%25e4%25be%258b%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%25ae%25b6&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM9%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=d9fa810f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200309%2Fs00005%2F1583712701180%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%2584%258f%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%2588%25a9%25e5%2596%25ae%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%25a2%259e133%25e6%25ad%25bb-%25e7%25b4%25af%25e8%25a8%25887375